sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Okta Inc (Symbol: OKTA), where a total of 9,766 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 976,600 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 44.8% of OKTA's average daily trading volume over the past month of 2.2 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $105 strike call option expiring May 17, 2019, with 2,493 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 249,300 underlying shares of OKTA.
